# Today Meal UI Design System

- Style direction: premium, warm, healing, creamy, minimal. Prefer generous whitespace, rounded cards, soft shadows, and warm brown accents.
- Core colors: primary `#B7895C`, primary light `#F5EAE2`, primary dark/pressed `#9F6E46`, page background `#FFF8F5`, card background `#FFFFFF`, divider `#EFE7E1`.
- Text colors: primary `#2D2520`, secondary `#8C7F76`, tertiary `#C5BEB8`. Status colors: success `#5FB878`, alert/tip `#FF6B6B`.
- Typography: Chinese `PingFang SC`; English can use SF Pro/DIN style. In rpx: hero title `56rpx`, page title `40rpx`, module title `32rpx`, body `28rpx`, helper `24rpx`, button `28rpx`.
- Radius tokens in rpx: tag/small button `16rpx`, input/small card `24rpx`, main card `32rpx`, large image card `48rpx`, circle `50%`.
- Spacing uses a 4px base grid, so use multiples of `8rpx`. Page horizontal padding `32rpx`, card padding `32rpx`, module spacing around `48rpx`.
- Shadows: light `0 4rpx 24rpx rgba(45,37,32,0.06)`, medium `0 8rpx 40rpx rgba(45,37,32,0.08)`.
- Buttons: primary height about `96rpx`, radius `24rpx`, background primary, white text. Secondary height about `80rpx`, radius `24rpx`, primary border/text.
