- Cards and lists: dish card radius `32rpx`, padding `32rpx`, image radius `24rpx`; list row target height around `176rpx`.
- Tags: height about `64rpx`, radius `32rpx`; selected uses primary-light background and primary text, inactive uses page background and secondary text.
- Product pages to preserve: home greeting, random recommendation card, quick recipe/takeout entries, inspiration horizontal list, filter chips, random result, recipe list, add form, and takeout favorites.
